title: Grateful Dead Live at Giants Stadium on 1995-06-18
description:
Set 1

Feel Like A Stranger, Bertha, The Same Thing, Stagger Lee, Eternity*, Deal

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Way To Go Home, Samson & Delilah, Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> Space-> Spanish Jam-> I Need A Miracle-> Wharf Rat-> Not Fade Away, E: Lucy In The Sky With Diamonds

* Weir on acoustic. Other Artist(s): Dylan openned
